<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　周易章句證異卷八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:223'>　　　　　　　　　　　内閣中書翟均㢘撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:230'>繫辭下𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='230:267'>　吳仁傑作説卦中<span class='krp-note'>見上馮/椅説</span>韓伯作繫詞下<span class='krp-note'>無𫝊字次/第八  陸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='267:317'>　<span class='krp-note'>徳明孔頴達周燔張浚李衡同張胡旦胡瑗王洙程/逈次第七  吕大防次第八    子次第四  以上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='317:359'>　<span class='krp-note'>无傳/字</span>王肅作繫詞下𫝊<span class='krp-note'>蘇子瞻朱震次第八第吕/祖謙朱子李宗𫝊次  六</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='359:379'>八卦成列象在其中矣因而重之爻在其中矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='379:405'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-1b' );" name="008-1b" class="pb">[008-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='405:427'>剛柔相推變在其中矣繫辭焉而命之動在其中矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='427:442'>　命孟喜作明<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/從明</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='442:454'>吉凶悔吝者生乎動者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='454:470'>剛柔者立本者也變通者趣時者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='470:479'>吉凶者貞勝者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='479:487'>　勝姚信作稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='487:510'>天地之道貞觀者也日月之道貞明者也天下之動貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='510:516'>夫一者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='516:542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-2a' );" name="008-2a" class="pb">[008-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='542:563'>　吳仁傑自八卦成列至貞夫一者也為第一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='563:581'>夫乾確然示人易矣夫坤隤然示人簡矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='581:614'>　確許慎作寉<span class='krp-note'>髙至也/惠棟同</span>　隤孟喜作退<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span>陸績董遇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='614:621'>　姚信作妥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='621:637'>爻也者效此者也象也者像此者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='637:654'>　像虞翻作象<span class='krp-note'>李鼎祚/惠棟同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='654:677'>爻象動乎内吉凶見乎外功業見乎變聖人之情見乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='677:680'>辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='680:706'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-2b' );" name="008-2b" class="pb">[008-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='706:730'>　郭雍朱震王宗𫝊王申子吳澄自八卦成列至見乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='730:738'>　詞為第一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='738:761'>天地之大徳曰生聖人之大寳曰位何以守位曰仁何</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='761:778'>以聚人曰財理財正辭禁民為非曰義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='778:813'>　寳孟喜作保　仁陸徳明作人<span class='krp-note'>晁説之本作人作吕/祖謙曰人今本  仁</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='813:862'>　<span class='krp-note'>當從釋文吳朱子作人云吕氏從古葢所謂非衆罔/與守邦    澄作人  俞琰曰上下文義詳之當依</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='862:901'>　<span class='krp-note'>作人/作人</span>　<span class='krp-note'>董楷徐在漢查慎行/靈格曰仁不必改人</span>王肅宋衷卞伯玉桓元</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='901:944'>　明僧紹作仁<span class='krp-note'>吴草廬以王卞桓明諸本作仁誤注孔/頴達李鼎祚諸儒作仁廉按鄭𤣥  禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='944:970'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-3a' );" name="008-3a" class="pb">[008-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='970:1018'>　<span class='krp-note'>運引作仁周書蘇綽𫝊引易作仁梁劉昭注後漢書/梁統𫝊引易作仁蔡邕亦云以仁守位知當時本作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1018:1066'>　<span class='krp-note'>仁李心𫝊曰蔡邕所云則漢前已用仁字非始于王/肅  毛竒齡曰釋文作人宋作偽古本從之致本義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1066:1096'>　<span class='krp-note'>以後多改/人字誤甚</span>　禁民漢書食貨志晉書刑法志引作人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1096:1127'>　<span class='krp-note'>李賢注梁統/𫝊引作人</span>　吳澄曰與上文不相屬當為下章之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1127:1150'>　首　龍仁夫曰五句恐是他經誤入　季本以將叛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1150:1178'>　者三十七字移置此下别為一章<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡曰何/无忌至此</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1178:1201'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達吕祖謙朱子項安世黄震董楷惠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1201:1217'>　棟自八卦成列至曰義為第一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1217:1243'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-3b' );" name="008-3b" class="pb">[008-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1243:1261'>　吳仁傑自夫乾確然至曰義為第二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1261:1284'>古者包犧氏之王天下也仰則觀象於天俯則觀法於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1284:1307'>地觀鳥獸之文與地之宜近取諸身遠取諸物於是始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1307:1324'>作八卦以通神明之徳以類萬物之情</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1324:1348'>　包孟喜京房作伏鄭𤣥作包虞翻作庖陸徳明曰本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1348:1377'>　又作庖<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚/惠棟同</span>　犧孟喜京房作戯陸徳明作羲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1377:1407'>　　王昭素曰與天地之宜諸本多有天字<span class='krp-note'>晁説之朱/子從其説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1407:1453'>　<span class='krp-note'>廉按班固藝文志作宓戯氏仰觀象於天俯觀法於/地觀鳥獸之文與地之宜又司馬貞史記補引此亦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1453:1479'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-4a' );" name="008-4a" class="pb">[008-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1479:1513'>　<span class='krp-note'>无天字九家易韓伯李鼎祚孔頴達/俱无天字王云多有天字不知何據</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1513:1530'>作結繩而為網罟以佃以漁蓋取諸離</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1530:1562'>　馬融虞翻姚信陸徳明李鼎祚作為罟<span class='krp-note'>無罔字馬云/猶网也  吕</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1562:1603'>　<span class='krp-note'>祖謙作為罟併惠棟作為罟云罟讀為/□古文二字  故誤也鍾鼎文皆然</span>黄頴乾鑿度</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1603:1646'>　作為□罟<span class='krp-note'>李氏心𫝊曰緯書出先漢既有罔字則隋/唐本無者非也廉按□古文作□時本亦</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1646:1683'>　<span class='krp-note'>作/網</span>　佃虞翻作田<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚惠棟同田陸/徳明曰佃本亦作</span>　漁虞翻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1683:1707'>　作魚<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚惠棟同魚陸/徳明曰漁本亦作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1707:1730'>包犧氏沒神農氏作斲木為耜揉木為耒耒耨之利以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1730:1756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-4b' );" name="008-4b" class="pb">[008-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1756:1765'>教天下蓋取諸益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1765:1788'>　包見上　陸徳明曰本或作揉木為耒耨非　耒耨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1788:1824'>　王昭素曰耨諸本或作耜<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰耜乃合上文右/吳澄作耜云𫝊冩者偽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1824:1844'>　<span class='krp-note'>傍㠯字為辱廉按/孟喜馬融本作耨</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1844:1867'>日中為市致天下之民聚天下之貨交易而退各得其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1867:1875'>所蓋取諸噬嗑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1875:1898'>神農氏沒黄帝堯舜氏作通其變使民不倦神而化之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1898:1921'>使民冝之易窮則變變則通通則久是以自天祐之吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1921:1947'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-5a' );" name="008-5a" class="pb">[008-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1947:1968'>无不利黄帝堯舜垂衣裳而天下治蓋取諸乾坤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1968:1991'>　陸徳明曰本亦作易窮則變通則久　吳澄无是以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1991:2024'>　自天祐之二句<span class='krp-note'>云十字繫文言釋大/有上九爻詞此重出</span>　祐見本卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2024:2047'>刳木為舟剡木為楫舟楫之利以濟不通致遠以利天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2047:2054'>下蓋取諸渙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2054:2089'>　刳九家易陸徳明李鼎祚作挎<span class='krp-note'>吕祖謙曰挎今本作/刳  董楷惠棟作挎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2089:2123'>　　剡九家易陸徳明李鼎祚作掞<span class='krp-note'>吕祖謙曰掞今本/作剡  董楷惠棟</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2123:2150'>　<span class='krp-note'>作/掞</span>　楫陸徳明曰本又作檝　陸徳明曰一本無致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2150:2176'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-5b' );" name="008-5b" class="pb">[008-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2176:2204'>　遠以利天下句　朱子曰致遠以利天下疑衍<span class='krp-note'>俞琰/從之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2204:2243'>　<span class='krp-note'>查慎曰似/不必從</span>吳澄刪此六字<span class='krp-note'>云此六字見下文重/出  陳仁錫刪此句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2243:2261'>服牛乗馬引重致遠以利天下蓋取諸隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2261:2303'>　服許慎作□<span class='krp-note'>晁説之音偹服俞琰曰史記伯□即左/傳伯服□與  通廣韵□有两音一音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2303:2351'>　<span class='krp-note'>服一音偹□但音偹不音服禮惠棟作□云古服字/孟喜作□鄭𤣥注特牲饋食  云古偹為復或作□</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2351:2374'>　<span class='krp-note'>古音/通也</span>　陸徳明曰一本無以利天下句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2374:2388'>重門擊柝以待暴客蓋取諸豫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2388:2437'>　柝許慎作柝又作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2190' title='KR2190' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2190.png'/><span class='krp-note'>晁說之曰今本説文出/此<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2190' title='KR2190' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2190.png'/>字非古本説文也</span>九家易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2437:2463'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-6a' );" name="008-6a" class="pb">[008-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2463:2504'>　作柝<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚/惠棟同</span>　暴鄭𤣥作虣<span class='krp-note'>荀九家易干寶李鼎/祚同  惠棟從虣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2504:2521'>　<span class='krp-note'>按朱彛尊毛竒/齡引鄭作虣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2521:2544'>㫁木為杵掘地為臼臼杵之利萬民以濟蓋取諸小過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2544:2564'>　掘虞翻作闕地為臼<span class='krp-note'>李鼎祚/惠棟同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2564:2586'>弦木為弧剡木為矢弧矢之利以威天下蓋取諸暌</span><br/>
