<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2609:2619'>待風雨葢取諸大壯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2619:2642'>古之葬者厚衣之以薪葬之中野不封不樹喪期无數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2642:2668'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-6b' );" name="008-6b" class="pb">[008-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2668:2684'>後世聖人易之以棺槨蓋取諸大過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2684:2715'>　班固作藏之中野<span class='krp-note'>見劉向𫝊/張釋之引</span>范奕引作古之葬者衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2715:2753'>　以藏之中野<span class='krp-note'>見趙咨𫝊古惠棟云塟/有作藏者  𦵏藏同音</span>　封虞翻云古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2753:2772'>　窆字　喪吕祖謙作□<span class='krp-note'>云今/作喪</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2772:2795'>上古結繩而治後世聖人易之以書契百官以治萬民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2795:2803'>以察蓋取諸夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2803:2811'>　世許慎作代</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2811:2834'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達朱子黄震董楷惠棟古者至蓋取</span><br/>
