<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2860:2869'>　諸夬為第二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2869:2888'>　王申子自天地之大徳至諸夬為第二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2888:2901'>是故易者象也象也者像也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2901:2924'>　像也孟喜京房虞翻董遇姚信崔憬李鼎祚作象陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2924:2936'>　徳明孔頴達諸本作像</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2936:2966'>　謹案　周易折中以此節為上章結語文<span class='krp-note'>云凡章首/不用是故</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2966:2992'>　<span class='krp-note'>是故承上結上之詞諸儒以此/節為上章結語近是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2992:2998'>彖者材也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2998:3024'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-7b' );" name="008-7b" class="pb">[008-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3024:3036'>爻也者效天下之動者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3036:3048'>是故吉凶生而悔吝著也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3048:3072'>　郭雍朱震王宗𫝊吳澄自天地之大徳至悔吝著也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='3072:3114'>　為第二章<span class='krp-note'>朱子曰胡旦分天地之大徳為一章陽卦/多隂為一章考之文義當從龔原本亦然</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='3114:3137'>　吕祖謙項安世自古者包犧氏之王天下也至悔吝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='3137:3154'>　著也為第二章<span class='krp-note'>云從晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3154:3177'>　朱子董楷惠棟自是故易者至悔吝著也為第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3177:3197'>　吳仁傑自是故易者至悔吝著也為第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3197:3223'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-8a' );" name="008-8a" class="pb">[008-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3223:3233'>陽卦多隂隂卦多陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3233:3245'>其故何也陽卦竒隂卦耦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3245:3260'>　俞琰曰五句疑錯簡當屬前章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3260:3283'>其徳行何也陽一君而二民君子之道也隂二君而一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3283:3291'>民小人之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3291:3314'>　俞琰曰其徳行何也一節疑錯簡當屬前章貞夫一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3314:3319'>　之下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3319:3342'>　朱子董楷惠棟自陽卦多隂至小人之道也為第四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3342:3368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-8b' );" name="008-8b" class="pb">[008-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3368:3372'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3372:3393'>　項安世自陽卦多隂至小人之道也為第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3393:3414'>　王申子自是故易者至小人之道也為第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3414:3437'>易曰憧憧徃來朋從爾思子曰天下何思何慮天下同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3437:3454'>歸而殊途一致而百慮天下何思何慮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3454:3468'>　憧見本爻　吳澄省子曰字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3468:3491'>日徃則月來月徃則日來日月相推而明生焉寒徃則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3491:3514'>暑來暑徃則寒來寒暑相推而嵗成焉徃者屈也來者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3514:3540'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-9a' );" name="008-9a" class="pb">[008-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3540:3552'>信也屈信相感而利生焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3552:3573'>　屈荀爽李鼎祚作詘　信陸徳明曰本又作伸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3573:3596'>尺蠖之屈以求信也龍蛇之蟄以存身也精義入神以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3596:3609'>致用也利用安身以崇徳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3609:3643'>　蛇陸徳明作虵<span class='krp-note'>惠棟本/從虵</span>　存身釋文作全身<span class='krp-note'>吕祖謙/云全身</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3643:3681'>　<span class='krp-note'>今作存身廉按李鼎祚云諸本作存身朱/本從釋文則知本義當作全今作存者悞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3681:3700'>過此以徃未之或知也窮神知化徳之盛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3700:3723'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達自是故易者象也至徳之盛也為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3723:3749'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-9b' );" name="008-9b" class="pb">[008-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3749:3755'>　第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3755:3779'>　熊朋來曰四節作咸九四文言　吳澄作文言𫝊四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3779:3805'>　章之一節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水云是文言此毛/竒齡云文言脱於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3805:3828'>易曰困于石據于蒺藜入于其宫不見其妻凶子曰非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3828:3851'>所困而困焉名必辱非所據而據焉身必危既辱且危</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3851:3863'>死期將至妻其可得見邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3863:3898'>　期陸績陸徳明作其<span class='krp-note'>期李心𫝊吳澄董楷作其/吕祖謙作其云今本作期</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3898:3922'>　熊朋來作困六三文言　吳澄為文言𫝊四章之六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3922:3949'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-10a' );" name="008-10a" class="pb">[008-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3949:3970'>　節省子曰字<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡亦云文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3970:3993'>易曰公用射隼于髙墉之上獲之无不利子曰隼者禽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3993:4016'>也弓矢者器也射之者人也君子藏器於身待時而動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='4016:4039'>何不利之有動而不括是以出而有獲語成器而動者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4039:4042'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4042:4066'>　熊朋來作觧上六文言　吳澄作文言𫝊四章之三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4066:4074'>　節省子曰字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4074:4097'>子曰小人不恥不仁不畏不義不見利不勸不威不懲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4097:4124'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-10b' );" name="008-10b" class="pb">[008-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4124:4147'>小懲而大誡此小人之福也易曰屨校滅趾无咎此之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4147:4151'>謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4151:4193'>　勸郭京作動<span class='krp-note'>云誤作勸凡悔吝所生由乎動者則是/小人見利而動  毛竒齡云勸與懲對</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4193:4226'>　<span class='krp-note'>待之文/郭京誤</span>　懲虞翻李鼎祚作徵<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span>　誡虞翻李鼎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4226:4232'>　祚作戒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4232:4256'>　熊朋來作噬嗑初九文言　吳澄作文言𫝊三章之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4256:4273'>　六節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4273:4296'>善不積不足以成名惡不積不足以滅身小人以小善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4296:4323'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-11a' );" name="008-11a" class="pb">[008-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4323:4346'>為无益而弗為也以小惡為无傷而弗去也故惡積而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4346:4364'>不可掩罪大而不可觧易曰何校滅耳凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4364:4381'>　掩虞翻李鼎祚作弇<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4381:4405'>　熊朋來作噬嗑上九文言　吳澄作文言𫝊三章之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4405:4423'>　七節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4423:4446'>子曰危者安其位者也亡者保其存者也亂者有其治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4446:4469'>者也是故君子安而不忘危存而不忘亡治而不忘亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4469:4491'>是以身安而國家可保也易曰其亡其亡繫于包桑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4491:4518'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-11b' );" name="008-11b" class="pb">[008-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4518:4537'>　漢書劉向𫝊引作安不忘危存不忘亡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4537:4561'>　熊朋來作否九五文言　吳澄作文言𫝊三章之一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4561:4582'>　節省子曰字<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4582:4605'>子曰徳薄而位尊知小而謀大力小而任重鮮不及矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4605:4625'>易曰鼎折足覆公餗其形渥凶言不勝其任也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4625:4662'>　知小虞翻李鼎祚作知少<span class='krp-note'>本按今李/  亦作小</span>力小同<span class='krp-note'>石經惟/力小作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4662:4700'>　<span class='krp-note'>少/</span>　鮮虞翻陸徳明李鼎祚作尟<span class='krp-note'>虞云尟少也謙董/楷同  吕祖  云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4700:4729'>　<span class='krp-note'>尟今作鮮俗惠棟云/尟亦作尠  作鮮</span>　餗形渥見本爻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4729:4756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-12a' );" name="008-12a" class="pb">[008-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4756:4780'>　熊朋來作鼎九四文言　吳澄作文言𫝊四章之七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4780:4801'>　節省子曰字<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4801:4824'>子曰知幾其神乎君子上交不諂下交不凟其知幾乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4824:4847'>幾者動之微吉之先見者也君子見幾而作不俟終日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4847:4870'>易曰介于石不終日貞吉介如石焉寧用終日㫁可識</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4870:4887'>矣君子知微知彰知柔知剛萬夫之望</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4887:4911'>　漢書楚元王𫝊引作吉凶之先見者也又藝文志引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4911:4940'>　易无凶字<span class='krp-note'>廉按兩/處不同</span>孔頴達云諸本或有凶字其定本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4940:4967'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-12b' );" name="008-12b" class="pb">[008-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4967:5008'>　則无<span class='krp-note'>向吉而背凶違凶而就吉无復有凶/故特云吉  二程子張子諸儒説同</span>朱子云漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='5008:5043'>　書吉之之間有凶字似是漏字<span class='krp-note'>吳澄増凶字同胡炳/文俞琰梁寅  朱子</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='5043:5074'>　<span class='krp-note'>説楊庭筠云象㫖曰朱子從漢書/非也廉按虞翻諸儒俱无凶字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='5074:5098'>　熊朋來作豫六二文言　吳澄作文言𫝊三章之五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='5098:5115'>　節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5115:5138'>子曰顔氏之子其殆庶幾乎有不善未嘗不知知之未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='5138:5154'>嘗復行也易曰不遠復无祇悔元吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='5154:5162'>　祇字見本爻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='5162:5189'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-13a' );" name="008-13a" class="pb">[008-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='5189:5213'>　熊朋來作復初九文言　吳澄作文言𫝊三章之八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5213:5234'>　節省子曰字<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5234:5257'>天地絪緼萬物化醇男女搆精萬物化生易曰三人行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5257:5274'>則損一人一人行則得其友言致一也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5274:5306'>　絪緼許慎作壹□李鼎祚作壹□<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡曰李鼎今/祚作紜廉按與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5306:5342'>　<span class='krp-note'>李本異□惠/棟作壹</span>陸徳明本又作氤氲<span class='krp-note'>查慎行曰絪/緼與氤氲同</span>後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5342:5367'>　漢書張衡𫝊引作烟煴班固𫝊注引蔡邕説作絪緼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5367:5411'>　<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰壹□篆文/絪緼古文氤氲𨽻文</span>　醇宋本亦作亨<span class='krp-note'>毛居正六經/正誤曰醇作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5411:5438'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-13b' );" name="008-13b" class="pb">[008-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5438:5467'>　<span class='krp-note'>亨/誤</span>　構鄭𤣥作覯<span class='krp-note'>云合也/惠棟同</span>　李衡作媾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5467:5491'>　熊朋來作損六三文言　吳澄作文言𫝊四章之四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5491:5508'>　節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5508:5531'>子曰君子安其心而後動易其心而後語定其交而後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5531:5554'>求君子修此三者故全也危以動則民不與也懼以語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5554:5577'>則民不應也无交而求則民不與也莫之與則傷之者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5577:5594'>至矣易曰莫益之或擊之立心勿恆凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5594:5624'>　危以動則民不與之與郭京作輔<span class='krp-note'>云輔助之/義誤作與</span>吳澄作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5624:5651'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-14a' );" name="008-14a" class="pb">[008-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5651:5670'>　興<span class='krp-note'>云與字與下文/重興應則韻叶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5670:5693'>　熊朋來作益上九文言　吳澄作文言傳四章之五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5693:5710'>　節<span class='krp-note'>湛若水毛竒/齡同作文言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5710:5733'>　朱震云張載曰下文當云易曰自天祐之吉无不利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5733:5756'>　子曰天之所助者順也人之所助者信也履信思乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5756:5776'>　順又以尚賢也是以自天祐之吉无不利也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5776:5799'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達自易曰困于石至立心勿恆凶為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5799:5805'>　第四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5805:5832'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-14b' );" name="008-14b" class="pb">[008-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5832:5856'>　朱震吕祖謙王宗𫝊自陽卦多隂至立心勿恆凶為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5856:5882'>　第三章<span class='krp-note'>朱云從胡旦龔原分章/吕云從晁説之分章</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5882:5905'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易曰憧憧徃來至立心勿恆凶為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5905:5911'>　第五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5911:5931'>　黄震自是故易者至立心勿恆凶為第三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5931:5952'>　吳仁傑自陽卦多隂至立心勿恆凶為第四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5952:5975'>　項安世王申子自易曰憧憧徃來至立心勿恆凶為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5975:5981'>　第四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5981:6008'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-15a' );" name="008-15a" class="pb">[008-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='6008:6031'>子曰乾坤其易之門邪乾陽物也坤隂物也隂陽合徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='6031:6050'>而剛柔有體以體天地之撰以通神明之徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='6050:6073'>　吳澄省子曰字　門邪陸徳明又作門户邪顔之推</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='6073:6082'>　家訓引作門户</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='6082:6102'>其稱名也雜而不越於稽其類其衰世之意邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='6102:6117'>　越許慎作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR2781' title='KR2781' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2781.png'/></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='6117:6140'>　吕祖謙吳仁傑自子曰乾坤其易之門邪至衰世之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='6140:6157'>　意邪為第四章<span class='krp-note'>云從晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='6157:6184'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-15b' );" name="008-15b" class="pb">[008-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='6184:6207'>夫易彰徃而察來而微顯闡幽開而當名辨物正言㫁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='6207:6213'>辭則備矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='6213:6236'>　彰虞翻李鼎祚作章　朱子曰而微顯恐當作微顯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='6236:6268'>　而開而之而亦疑有誤<span class='krp-note'>葉爾瞻曰三而多/有着落似无誤</span>　李鼎祚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='6268:6294'>　以開而當名㫁節何楷開當<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>名辨物正<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='6294:6317'>其稱名也小其取類也大其㫖遠其辭文其言曲而中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='6317:6336'>其事肆而隱因貳以濟民行以明失得之報</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='6336:6361'>　貳鄭𤣥云當為弍<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰/弍古文</span>虞翻作二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='6361:6388'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-16a' );" name="008-16a" class="pb">[008-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='6388:6411'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達項安世自乾坤其易之門邪至以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6411:6423'>　明失得之報為第五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6423:6447'>　朱震王宗𫝊黄震自乾坤其易之門邪至以明失得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6447:6456'>　之報為第四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6456:6479'>　吕祖謙吳仁傑自夫易彰徃而察來至以明失得之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6479:6495'>　報為第五章<span class='krp-note'>云從晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6495:6518'>　朱子董楷惠棟自乾坤其易之門邪至以明失得之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6518:6526'>　報為第六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6526:6553'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-16b' );" name="008-16b" class="pb">[008-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6553:6581'>　吳澄自陽卦多隂至以明失得之報為第四章<span class='krp-note'>按澄/以陽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6581:6628'>　<span class='krp-note'>卦多隂四十五字移置乾坤其易之門上云小人之/道也舊有文言𫝊釋錯簡十一節間隔之故與乾坤</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6628:6675'>　<span class='krp-note'>其易之門不相屬遂于乾坤上加子曰字而分為别/章今定錯簡歸文言𫝊刪去子曰字而此章復合為</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6675:6682'>　<span class='krp-note'>一/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6682:6701'>易之興也其于中古乎作易者其有憂患乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6701:6724'>　王申子自乾坤其易之門邪至其有憂患乎為第五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6724:6728'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6728:6751'>是故履徳之基也謙徳之柄也復徳之本也恆徳之固</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6751:6778'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-17a' );" name="008-17a" class="pb">[008-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6778:6801'>也損徳之脩也益徳之裕也困徳之辨也井徳之地也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6801:6808'>巽徳之制也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6808:6829'>　脩馬融作循　辨鄭𤣥陸徳明李鼎祚作辯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6829:6852'>履和而至謙尊而光復小而辨于物恆雜而不厭損先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6852:6875'>難而後易益長裕而不設困窮而通井居其所而遷巽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6875:6880'>稱而隱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6880:6903'>履以和行謙以制禮復以自知恆以一徳損以遠害益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6903:6920'>以興利困以寡怨井以辨義巽以行權</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6920:6947'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-17b' );" name="008-17b" class="pb">[008-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6947:6970'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達吕祖謙項安世自易之興也至巽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6970:6989'>　以行權為第六章<span class='krp-note'>吕云從/晁説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6989:7013'>　朱震黄震王宗𫝊自易之興也至巽以行權為第五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='7013:7017'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='7017:7040'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易之興也至巽以行權為第七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='7040:7059'>　王申子自是故履至巽以行權為第六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='7059:7078'>　吳澄自易之興也至巽以行權為第四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='7078:7101'>易之為書也不可遠為道也屢遷變動不居周流六虚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='7101:7128'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-18a' );" name="008-18a" class="pb">[008-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='7128:7147'>上下无常剛柔相易不可為典要惟變所適</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='7147:7159'>其出入以度外内使知懼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='7159:7191'>　朱子本義曰此句未詳疑有脱誤<span class='krp-note'>語録云據文勢合/作使内外知懼</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='7191:7208'>又明於憂患與故无有師保如臨父母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='7208:7230'>初率其辭而揆其方既有典常茍非其人道不虚行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='7230:7256'>　率虞翻作帥<span class='krp-note'>云率正也棟李鼎/祚同  惠  同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='7256:7279'>　朱震黄震自易之為書也不可遠至道不虚行為第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='7279:7291'>　六章<span class='krp-note'>云從/龔原</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='7291:7318'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-18b' );" name="008-18b" class="pb">[008-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='7318:7341'>　吕祖謙項安世王申子自易之為書也不可遠至道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='7341:7360'>　不虚行為第七章<span class='krp-note'>吕云從/晁説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='7360:7383'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易之為書也不可遠至道不虚行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='7383:7390'>　為第八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='7390:7413'>　吳澄自易之為書也不可遠至道不虚行為第五章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7413:7436'>易之為書也原始要終以為質也六爻相雜唯其時物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7436:7439'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7439:7460'>其初難知其上易知本末也初辭擬之卒成之終</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7460:7487'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-19a' );" name="008-19a" class="pb">[008-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7487:7506'>若夫雜物撰徳辨是與非則非其中爻不備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7506:7521'>　撰鄭𤣥作算<span class='krp-note'>云數/也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7521:7544'>噫亦要存亡吉凶則居可知矣知者觀其彖辭則思過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7544:7548'>半矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7548:7571'>　噫王肅於力反陸徳明於其反　亦要陸徳明曰一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7571:7587'>　妙反絶句又一遥反則句至吉凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7587:7608'>　季本以噫字下二十三字移置其剛勝邪之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7608:7631'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達朱震自易之為書也原始要終至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7631:7658'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-19b' );" name="008-19b" class="pb">[008-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7658:7669'>　思過半矣為第七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7669:7692'>二與四同功而異位其善不同二多譽四多懼近也柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7692:7710'>之為道不利遠者其要无咎其用柔中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7710:7733'>　郭京曰注云懼近也今本誤以近也字為正文近字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7733:7775'>　仍脱懼字<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡云案今王注已無懼近也句而康/伯所注仍有四近于君故多懼語則直是</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7775:7789'>　<span class='krp-note'>經文豈可/妄為之説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7789:7812'>三與五同功而異位三多凶五多功貴賤之等也其柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7812:7819'>危其剛勝邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7819:7846'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-20a' );" name="008-20a" class="pb">[008-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7846:7875'>　朱震自二與四同功至其剛勝邪為第八章<span class='krp-note'>云龔本/原始要</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='7875:7897'>　<span class='krp-note'>終合易之為書也為/一章誤矣今從故本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7897:7920'>　吕祖謙項安世吳仁傑王申子自易之為書也原始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7920:7934'>　要終至其剛勝邪為第八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7934:7957'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易之為書也原始要終至其剛勝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7957:7965'>　邪為第九章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7965:7988'>　黄震自易之為書也原始要終至其剛勝邪為第七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7988:7992'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='7992:8019'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-20b' );" name="008-20b" class="pb">[008-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='8019:8042'>　吳澄自易之為書也原始要終至其剛勝邪為第六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='8042:8046'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='8046:8069'>易之為書也廣大悉備有天道焉有人道焉有地道焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='8069:8089'>兼三才而兩之故六六者非它也三才之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='8089:8097'>　才石經作材</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='8097:8120'>道有變動故曰爻爻有等故曰物物相雜故曰文文不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='8120:8128'>當故吉凶生焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='8128:8151'>　吕祖謙項安世王申子吳仁傑自易之為書也廣大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='8151:8178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-21a' );" name="008-21a" class="pb">[008-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='8178:8201'>　悉備至故吉凶生焉為第九章<span class='krp-note'>云從晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='8201:8224'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易之為書也廣大悉備至故吉凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='8224:8233'>　生焉為第十章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='8233:8256'>　黄震自易之為書也廣大悉備至故吉凶生焉為第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='8256:8261'>　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='8261:8285'>　王宗𫝊自易之為書也廣大悉備至故吉凶生焉為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='8285:8291'>　第六章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='8291:8314'>　吳澄自易之為書也廣大悉備至故吉凶生焉為第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='8314:8341'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-21b' );" name="008-21b" class="pb">[008-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='8341:8346'>　七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='8346:8369'>易之興也其當殷之末世周之盛徳邪當文王與紂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='8369:8392'>事邪是故其辭危危者使平易者使傾其道甚大百物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='8392:8411'>不廢懼以終始其要无咎此之謂易之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='8411:8434'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達自二與四同功至易之道也為第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='8434:8439'>　八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='8439:8462'>　朱震自易之為書也廣大悉備至易之道也為第九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='8462:8466'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='8466:8493'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-22a' );" name="008-22a" class="pb">[008-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='8493:8516'>　吕祖謙項安世王申子吳仁傑自易之興也至易之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='8516:8533'>　道也為第十章<span class='krp-note'>云從晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='8533:8556'>　朱子董楷惠棟自易之興也至易之道也為第十一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='8556:8560'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='8560:8579'>　黄震自易之興也至易之道也為第九章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='8579:8602'>夫乾天下之至健也徳行恒易以知險夫坤天下之至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='8602:8613'>順也徳行恆簡以知阻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='8613:8636'>能説諸心能研諸侯之慮定天下之吉凶成天下之亹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='8636:8663'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-22b' );" name="008-22b" class="pb">[008-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='8663:8667'>亹者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='8667:8690'>　王昭素曰剰侯之二字必是王輔嗣以後鄭康伯以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='8690:8735'>　前錯<span class='krp-note'>司馬温公曰王輔嗣畧例曰能研諸慮則侯之/衍字  張子朱震郭雍朱子吳澄衍侯之二字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='8735:8773'>　虞翻韓伯有侯之二字<span class='krp-note'>虞云乾初之坤為震震為諸/侯故能研諸侯之慮  晁説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='8773:8813'>　<span class='krp-note'>之曰虞翻亦作諸侯其謬久矣天毛竒齡曰/諸侯之慮即天下之慮與前後  下相應</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='8813:8833'>是故變化云為吉事有祥象事知器占事知來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='8833:8843'>　祥李鼎祚亦作詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='8843:8861'>天地設位聖人成能人謀鬼神百姓與能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='8861:8888'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-23a' );" name="008-23a" class="pb">[008-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='8888:8911'>　吳仁傑自夫乾天下之至健也至百姓與能為第十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='8911:8916'>　一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='8916:8938'>八卦以象告爻彖以情言剛柔雜居而吉凶可見矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='8938:8961'>　吳仁傑自八卦以象告至而吉凶可見矣為第十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='8961:8965'>　章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='8965:8988'>變動以利言吉凶以情遷是故愛惡相攻而吉凶生遠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='8988:9011'>近相取而悔吝生情偽相感而利害生凡易之情近而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='9011:9024'>不相得則凶或害之悔且吝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='9024:9051'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-23b' );" name="008-23b" class="pb">[008-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='9051:9065'>　王弼李鼎祚則凶<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='9065:9086'>　吳仁傑自變動以利言至悔且吝為第十三章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='9086:9109'>將叛者其辭慙中心疑者其辭枝吉人之辭寡躁人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='9109:9127'>辭多誣善之人其辭㳺失其守者其辭屈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='9127:9158'>　屈侯果李鼎祚作誳　馮椅曰此節錯簡<span class='krp-note'>與易全不/相闗  王</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='9158:9173'>　<span class='krp-note'>介甫郭子和/亦嘗疑之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='9173:9196'>　周氏莊氏孔頴達自夫乾天下之至健也至末為第</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='9196:9201'>　九章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='9201:9228'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-24a' );" name="008-24a" class="pb">[008-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='9228:9250'>　朱震黄震自夫乾天下之至健也至末為第十章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='9250:9273'>　吕祖謙項安世王申子自夫乾天下之至健也至末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='9273:9281'>　為第十一章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='9281:9304'>　朱子董楷惠棟自夫乾天下之至健也至末為第十</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='9304:9309'>　二章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='9309:9327'>　王宗𫝊自易之興也至末為第七章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='9327:9343'>　吳澄自易之興也至末為第八章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='9343:9362'>　吳仁傑自將叛者至其辭屈為第十四章</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='9362:9389'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-24b' );" name="008-24b" class="pb">[008-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='9389:9414'>　吳澄曰繫詞𫝊上下篇共二十章章首𤼵端以天地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='9414:9437'>　字者三以聖人字者二以易字者十一以彖爻以一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='9437:9460'>　隂一陽以八卦以陽卦以隂卦者各一舊本有子曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='9460:9483'>　者六先儒以為後人所加今考之易其至矣乎知變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='9483:9506'>　化之道者其知神之所為乎皆是前章之結語後之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='9506:9529'>　分章者欲以此為後章之起語書不盡言乾坤其易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='9529:9552'>　之門邪皆是連上文共為一章後之分章者欲分截</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='9552:9575'>　自此别為一章故四處加子曰字以别之易有聖人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='9575:9602'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '008-25a' );" name="008-25a" class="pb">[008-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='9602:9625'>　之道四焉者是再提章首起句為結句聖人立象以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='9625:9648'>　盡意是以答語答上文問語故兩處亦各加子曰字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='9648:9672'>　今並刪去庶俾讀者不致生疑而妄謂繫辭𫝊非夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='9672:9679'>　子所作云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='9679:9682'>　</span><br/>
